    <div style=3D"font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; color:#33415c; margin-top=
:10px;">May 2026 delivered a strong top-line collections performance, with Ou=
t-of-Term (OOT) collections rising to R4.38m (+R0.54m MoM) and the overall Co=
llection Rate beating its target by 5.8pp at 33.5%. Early-stage (MP0) momentu=
m was a particular bright spot, with both yield and payer rate climbing 2.5pp=
 MoM to 50.0% and 50.7% respectively. However, late-stage and new loan segmen=
ts weakened notably, and Effort Yield fell short of target, areas that will r=
equire focused attention heading into June.</div>
